title: Grilling Stations, Rooftop Pet Park, Uber-Chic Rooftop Deck
posting_body: This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 618 Sq.
West Seattle’s newest apartment community offers a mix of studio, one- and two-bedroom apartments, plus two-bedroom townhomes and live/work units.
To live at Aura West Seattle is to live locally inspired by West Seattle’s laid-back culture yet be actively connected to everything Seattle has to offer.

Private Patios or Balconies*, Modern Lighting Throughout Apartment, In-Home Stacked Full-Size Washer/Dryer, Wood-Style Flooring, Modern Urban Residences, Quartz Countertops, Custom Carpeted Bedrooms, Amazing Seattle Skyline Views*, Walk-In Closets*, Whirlpool® Stainless Steel Appliances, Kitchens Designed for the "Foodie", Under-Mount "Farm Style" Sink, 2" Window Coverings Throughout, Soaring 10' Ceilings at Penthouse Level, Expansive Floor-to-Ceiling Windows in Living Spaces, Pendant Lighting Over Kitchen Bars/Islands, Danze® Spring Pull Down Faucet, Custom Cabinetry with Soft-Close Doors and Drawers Offered in Two Color Schemes

Uber-Chic Rooftop Deck, Multi-Size Storage Lockers Available, Package Acceptance with 24-7 Parcel Package Lockers, Access to West Seattle Hill Climb, WiFi in All Common Areas, Energizing Fitness Center with Cardio Theater and Free Weights, Resident Lounge and Social Gathering Area with Coffee Bar, Social Gathering Spaces, Onsite Bike and Pet Washing Station, RapidRide
Stop Right Outside Your Front Door.

One-Stop (10 minutes) to Downtown Seattle, Rooftop Pet Park, Climate Controlled Interior Corridors, Bike Storage, 24-Hour Maintenance Emergency Service, Multi-Level Parking Garage with Plenty of Parking for All Your Vehicles, Grilling Stations, Personal Gardening Spaces
We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.
